summary: Certified Scrum Master with an entrepreneurial commercial mindset and project management skills who drive gains in revenue and profit through customer satisfaction, retention, and seeking new sales opportunities. Results-oriented and high-energy professional with a talent for leading by example and inspiring excellence. Forward-thinking, responsive spirit with five years of entrepreneurial experience in the FMCG industry and 2 years in the e-com fashion industry with a focus on omnichannel marketing. Fourteen years of combined experience in all areas of business and of course a proven track record of completing projects on time within budget and creating new business opportunities.
